Miller's grieving parents

02:13.698 --> 02:15.613
is the best idea, but,
you know, if it comes to it...

02:15.657 --> 02:17.049
If it does,
we got your back.

02:18.790 --> 02:20.140
She's got your back.Oh. [ Laughs ]

02:20.183 --> 02:21.053
