anyone's back.

02:21.097 --> 02:22.533
[ Laughing ] Oh.

02:22.577 --> 02:23.621
Maddox: What were you gonna
do before you decided

02:23.665 --> 02:25.188
to join the Academy?

02:25.232 --> 02:26.537
High school teacher.

02:26.581 --> 02:27.973
