[ Laughs ]

02:34.719 --> 02:36.417
Dude. No, man.

02:36.460 --> 02:38.810
Stop.What?

02:38.854 --> 02:40.072
You got a sub
for today?

02:40.116 --> 02:42.292
I did, and please
keep in mind

02:42.336 --> 02:45.121
that there weren't
a lot of choices.

02:45.165 --> 02:47.993
[ Indistinct chatter ][ Both laugh ]

02:48.037 --> 02:50.213
Hey.

02:50.257 --> 02:52.694
If you don't step up to them,
it's only gonna get worse.

02:52.737 --> 02:54.217
It's a hazing thing.
It's fine.

02:54.261 --> 02:56.176
I can take it.
I know you can.
That's not the point.

02:56.219 --> 02:57.786
If I say something,
that puts me on the outside.

02:57.829 --> 02:59.614
That's not true.
It is.

02:59.657 --> 03:01.659
It is for you.

03:01.703 --> 03:04.532
Wow.Truth hurts.

03:04.575 --> 03:06.708
Oh!Gosh darn it!

03:06.751 --> 03:08.405
